                INITIALIZE REG-BPCFCENT  XML-OUTPUT
                PERFORM P300-OPEN-TAG-crc
                PERFORM P300-GERA-TAG-controlo
                PERFORM P300-OPEN-TAG-conteudo
                PERFORM P300-OPEN-TAG-comEnt
                SET CICLO-N TO TRUE
              END-IF
           END-IF
           IF SEM-ERRO
              PERFORM P300-OPEN-TAG-infEnt
     š*- i1 - Residente  / i2 - Não Residente
              PERFORM P300-GERA-TAG-idEnt
     š*- t1 - Particular
